claim.claim-text:
35. An instrumented pin member, comprising: 
a pin member body disposed about a pin member axis, the pin member body comprising a bending portion; 
a sensing device positioned on the pin member body within the bending portion for sensing a bending stress in the bending portion during a bending stress measurement mode and for outputting a sensor measurement signal; 
a switching device operatively coupled to the sensing device for switching the sensing device in and out of the bending stress measurement mode; and 
a sensor signal output device for communicating the sensor measurement signal.
